scene.message:
Nanjo: A black market, hm...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
A fitting name for this{nl}
desolate town.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: So the doctor's{nl}
normal...{waitkey}{clearbox}I was sweating bullets{nl}
wondering what I'd do if he{nl}
were some bald guy with an{nl}
eyepatch!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: What. I was expecting{nl}
a doctor with a bit more{nl}
impact.{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: I'm this happy all{nl}
thanks to the Harem Queen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's thank the Queen{nl}
together — Your Majesty,{nl}
thank you so very much!{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: My happiness wasn't{nl}
thanks to the Queen after{nl}
all!{waitkey}{clearbox}So then, what is it I have{nl}
to thank for my happiness?{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Now then, what'll{nl}
it be?{nl}
{ctl0e:17}{ret}

Doctor: It'll cost 1500 yen.{nl}
Is that all right?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Doctor: A shame, but I can't{nl}
treat you with no money...{nl}
Come back with the fee.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Skimp on treatment{nl}
now, and I hope it won't{nl}
come back to bite you.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: I'm a busy man. If{nl}
you've no business here,{nl}
off you go.{waitkey}{ret}
